/* Redirect all routes to index.html for SPA */
/*
   This ensures that client-side routing works by serving index.html for any path that does not match a static file.
*/
/*
   The format is: <source>   <destination>   <status>
   Example: /*   /index.html   200
*/
/*
   Place this file at the project root.
*/
/*
   Netlify automatically picks up this file when publishing.
*/
/*
   The essential redirect line:
*/
/*
   /*    /index.html   200
*/
